### T?i ?u hi?u n?ng

#### ProcessesTab.cs
```csharp
// Async loading ?? không block UI
public async Task LoadProcessesAsync()
{
    allProcesses = await Task.Run(() => 
        processMonitor.GetAllProcesses());
}

// Double buffering cho DataGridView
dataGridViewProcesses.DoubleBuffered(true);

// BindingList thay vì BindingSource.ResetBindings()
```

#### PerformanceTab.cs
```csharp
