#### Form1.cs
```csharp
// Prevent concurrent updates
private bool isUpdating = false;

private async Task UpdateAllDataAsync()
{
    if (isUpdating) return;
    isUpdating = true;
    try
    {
        // Only update active tab
        if (tabControl.SelectedTab == tabProcesses)
            await processesTab.LoadProcessesAsync();
        
        await performanceTab.UpdatePerformanceAsync();
    }
    finally
    {
        isUpdating = false;
    }
}
```

### ProcessMonitor.cs
- `GetAllProcesses()`: L?y danh sách processes v?i error handling
- `GetCpuUsage()`: Tính CPU d?a trên delta time
- `GetSystemInfo()`: Thông tin t?ng quan h? th?ng
- `KillProcess()`: K?t thúc process an toàn
- `Cleanup()`: Gi?i phóng tài nguyên

### Color Scheme

```csharp
// Primary colors
Blue:   #0D6EFD (13, 110, 253)   // CPU, Headers, Buttons
Green:  #198754 (25, 135, 84)    // RAM, Success
